{"id":2553,"date":"2023-03-09T15:07:24","date_gmt":"2023-03-09T08:07:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2553"},"modified":"2023-09-18T15:09:13","modified_gmt":"2023-09-18T08:09:13","slug":"quan-tri-khach-san-san-sang-cho-su-nghiep-4-0-toan-cau","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/quan-tri-khach-san-san-sang-cho-su-nghiep-4-0-toan-cau\/","title":{"rendered":"QU\u1ea2N TR\u1eca KH\u00c1CH S\u1ea0N &#8211; S\u1eb4N S\u00c0NG CHO S\u1ef0 NGHI\u1ec6P 4.0 TO\u00c0N C\u1ea6U"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 ng\u00e0nh \u201cc\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3i\u201d v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, m\u1edf ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><b>\u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><b><i>\u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n &#8211; T\u1ef1 tin ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh, v\u00e0 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh cho sinh vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n ki\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n 3 sao theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a ASEAN, x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 19 c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc t\u01b0 th\u1ee5c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Asean+ 2023 <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(AppliedHE).<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n nh\u1ea5t, sinh vi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i sinh ho\u1ea1t ngo\u1ea1i kh\u00f3a, workshop, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u00e0 giao l\u01b0u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn s\u00e2u r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1edfi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ng\u00e0nh, \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c kinh doanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u1ec1 Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-12592 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/IMG_5564-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><b><i>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o:<\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng m\u1ec1m, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p; ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc b\u1eb1ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p.\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Khi theo h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 sinh vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf du l\u1ecbch l\u1edbn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia k\u1ef3 th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c Du l\u1ecbch &#8211; Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n nh\u01b0: Sun World thu\u1ed9c t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Sun Group, T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Novotel, T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Continental&#8230;.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><b><i>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i:<\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ng\u1eafn, t\u0103ng th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. N\u0103m 2023, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh c\u00e1c su\u1ea5t h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n trong th\u1eddi gian theo h\u1ecdc, bao g\u1ed3m H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng T\u00e0i n\u0103ng d\u00e0nh 03 su\u1ea5t mi\u1ec5n 100% H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 2&amp;3 v\u00e0 H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh 05 su\u1ea5t mi\u1ec5n 100% h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 2.\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11379 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/3-2-1024x486.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"486\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11375 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/5-1-1024x486.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"486\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><b>Tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p:\u00a0<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">L\u0129nh v\u1ef1c Du l\u1ecbch &#8211; Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n &#8211; Nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n sau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea1i d\u1ecbch k\u00e9o d\u00e0i. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c Du l\u1ecbch Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Li\u00ean H\u1ee3p Qu\u1ed1c (UNWTO), hi\u1ec7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 6 trong s\u1ed1 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn du l\u1ecbch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nhanh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c1. M\u1ed7i n\u0103m, to\u00e0n ng\u00e0nh c\u1ea7n th\u00eam g\u1ea7n 40.000 lao \u0111\u1ed9ng, tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 20.000 lao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, \u0111\u00e1ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 1.800 sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, theo b\u00e1o c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng c\u1ee5c Du l\u1ecbch (2017). Nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c ng\u00e0nh Du l\u1ecbch, Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f2n y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ea5p trung v\u00e0 cao c\u1ea5p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh Du l\u1ecbch \u2013 Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, thu nh\u1eadp h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u00f9ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 v\u1ecb th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb thay th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng 4.0, sau khi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p, sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng \u2013 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb ti\u1ec1n s\u1ea3nh (Front Office)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb h\u1eadu s\u1ea3nh (Back Office)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn Nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng (Food &amp; Beverage)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn Bu\u1ed3ng ph\u00f2ng (Housekeeping)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kinh doanh v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh, ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb, nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty du l\u1ecbch<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Kinh doanh du l\u1ecbch trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn F&amp;B, Bartender, gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t, b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng\u2026 ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ea5p c\u01a1 s\u1edf t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng, kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, khu ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh kinh doanh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">Th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n, v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng trong ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c c\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, sinh vi\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><b>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">N\u0103m 2023, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 tuy\u1ec3n sinh ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u1edbi 03 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc b\u1ea1 THPT<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n 03 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3: T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 03 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a 03 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 (k\u1ef3 1,2 l\u1edbp 11 + k\u1ef3 1 l\u1edbp 12) + \u0110i\u1ec3m \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) \u2265 18,0 \u0111i\u1ec3m;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo t\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p 03 m\u00f4n: T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 03 m\u00f4n n\u0103m l\u1edbp 12 + \u0110i\u1ec3m \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) \u2265 18,0 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 k\u1ef3 thi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><b>C\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch 1: Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00e1t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh &#8211; <\/strong>T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, <strong>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Hotline: 0934.078.668 &#8211; \u00a0024.33.861.601<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch 2: Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i: <strong>Website:<\/strong> <strong><a href=\"http:\/\/www.thanhdo.edu.vn\">thanhdo.edu.vn<\/a><\/strong> ho\u1eb7c <strong>Fanpage: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\">\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/a><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/#dangkyxettuyen\"><img loading=